{"id":147299,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/04/简讯：北京警方拘押守望教会成员/","date":"2011-04-24T22:00:35Z","modified":"2011-04-24T22:00:35Z","title":"简讯：北京警方拘押守望教会成员","content":"<div>\n<p>北京警方星期日（4月24日）在中关村带走了10至20余名参加复活节宗教仪式的守望教会成员。</p>\n<p>路透社记者说，警方不让记者接近被拘押的教会成员。</p>\n<p>报告还说，被拘捕的教会成员没有抵抗。</p>\n<p>守望教会的牧师金天明近日来一直被当局软禁在家中。</p>\n</p></div>\n<div>\n<div>\n<p>\t<a href=\"http://www.bbc.co.uk/zhongwen/simp/china/2011/04/#page-top\" rel=\"nofollow\"><br />\n\t\t<span>点击</span><br />\n\t\t<span>页首</span><br />\n\t</a></div>\n</div>\n<p><a href=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/wZ49YPYoon6cRCC6t9RjHu_D6Kg/0/da\"><img border=\"0\" ismap src=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/wZ49YPYoon6cRCC6t9RjHu_D6Kg/0/di\"></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/wZ49YPYoon6cRCC6t9RjHu_D6Kg/1/da\"><img border=\"0\" ismap src=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/wZ49YPYoon6cRCC6t9RjHu_D6Kg/1/di\"></a></p>\n<p><img height=\"1\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/cnbbc/~4/In2Q_cqcDyA\" width=\"1\" /></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/f.fbz?AddNewUserDirect\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/?Sub=750556\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a> <br /><input name=\"EMAIL\" maxlength=\"64\" type=\"text\" size=\"25\" value=\"\"><br />\n<input name=\"FEEDID\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"750556\"><br />\n<input name=\"PUBLISHER\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"7485568\"><br />\n<input type=\"submit\" value=\"订阅!\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":176,"categories":[8779],"tags":[]}